{"tid":506910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥明詩收拾心情玩制服誘惑","createTime":"2017-12-22T16:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T08:10:10.000Z","uid":389,"like":105,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b821d5697268c80776ca86175aa4eac0a9fb6d","tid":506910,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/23/001935_4384da60fe995bca061a38b353c0493a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F23%2F001935_4384da60fe995bca061a38b353c0493a.jpg&h=1785ddbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麥明詩早前自爆大學時到內地參加交流團曾被性侵，遭網友質疑「抽水」，她遂於日前在社交網站上載一張向警方要求取回當年在長沙灣警署報稱非禮的口供副本的回覆信件。雖然警方回覆指該口供副本已被銷毁，但麥明詩以白紙黑字力證自己並沒「老作」，呼籲大家減少網絡審判。<br />\n<br />\n「神隱」數天後，麥明詩再度活躍社交網站，更上載了一張與港姐師妹馮盈盈的合照，二人分別穿上一藍一紅的水手校服，加上白滑長腿，散發陣陣仙氣，並留言說：「那些年的青春歲月。」照片一出隨即電暈一眾宅男，紛紛投票二人更有「女朋友味」，認真搞笑！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/1095755/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fent%2F1095755%2F&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9267f34e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fent%2F1095755%2F&h=e89d2e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/1095755/</a>"},{"pid":"558ccbedd97a79f390170ab113eb894d11d7c961","tid":506910,"uid":71315,"like":322,"dislike":14,"score":308,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"老實說麥明詩真係普通樣"},{"pid":"d6aba36d8e80be78d9aa289fc183f5407e4e0305","tid":506910,"uid":26156,"like":139,"dislike":31,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25e4eb47a0716b1a48a141ba5175db44dacb0716","tid":506910,"uid":19454,"like":144,"dislike":43,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/012340_074c446dde6a8f8ad3fc5